@page
@model ProductDetailsModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Product Details";
}

<div class="section-card">
    <h1>Jersey Details</h1>
    <p>
        This page would display the full details of the selected jersey, including images, description,
        available sizes, jersey number selection, quantity, and related options from the same national team.
    </p>
    <p>
        It would also include recommendations such as similar products and suggestions based on customer interest.
    </p>
    <p>
        This is also the page where the customer would choose size, number, quantity, and add the item to the cart.
    </p>
    <p>
        <em>@Model.ProductMessage</em>
    </p>
</div>